## DBchapter(Techniques of integration)
## DBsection(Integration by parts (with trigonometric functions))
## Institution(W.H.Freeman)
## Author(Christopher Sira)
## MLT(parts_01)
## Level(3)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus: Early Transcendentals 2e')
